entry.name: Radius Of Rotation
entry.definition: Distance to the center of detector rotation.

entry.name: Detector Count Zone
entry.definition: FOV zone for count-based acquisition termi- nation criteria. The Defined Terms are: 0 = none specified 1 = total (all) counts 2 = counts in energy set 3 = counts inside an ROI 4 = counts outside an ROI

entry.name: Num Energy Windows
entry.definition: Number of energy windows in energy set.

entry.name: Image Orientation
entry.definition: Orientation of the image. The Defined Terms are: 0 = no rotation, no mirroring 1 = no rotation, mirrored

entry.name: Table Orientation
entry.definition: Orientation of the table for whole body acquisition. The Defined Terms are: 0 = direction in/out 1 = direction left/right

entry.name: ROI Top Left
entry.definition: Acquisition count zone ROI, top left coordi- nate.

entry.name: ROI Bottom Right
entry.definition: Acquisition count zone ROI, bottom right coordinate.

entry.name: Tuning Calib Name
entry.definition: Name of applied tuning calibration data.

entry.name: Acquisition Specific Correct Name
entry.definition: Name(s) of associated acquisition specific correction(s).
